        {
            "title": "美國SEC擬修訂信息披露規則 呼應特朗普半年報建議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"SEC主席Paul AtkinsPhotographer: Stefani Reynolds/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4r9Ag_ooUltn86nFOq7uLQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9d925ebaa15de5cfefc7ad172269ad02\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">SEC主席Paul AtkinsPhotographer: Stefani Reynolds/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 美國證券交易委員會(SEC)主席Paul Atkins周五表示，證監會將推進改革上市公司投資者信息披露規則的計畫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一消息發布的同一周，美國總統特朗普在社交媒體上發文，建議SEC從季度財報制度改為半年報制度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Atkins在接受CNBC採訪時表示：「現在正是時候全面審視人們獲取信息的各種方式、信息的傳播途徑，以及哪種方式符合目的。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他指出，許多投資者更多地依賴財報電話會獲取信息，而不是季度報告。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-08e8bfbc-50db-3f56-b24b-13ff054d1220-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Atkins呼應了特朗普提出的批評，認為季度財報讓企業高管和管理層過於關注短期回報。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題SEC Will Move to Overhaul Investor Disclosure Rules, Atkins Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bsec%E6%93%AC%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87-%E5%91%BC%E6%87%89%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%A0%B1%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0-140237835.html",
